definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in East Devon district, Devon , England , the site of Membury Castle ( OS grid ref ST2703 ) .

A hamlet in Ramsbury parish, north-east Wiltshire , England ( OS grid ref SU3074 ) ; Membury services on the M4 motorway are nearby, but across the county boundary in West Berkshire . The site of Membury Camp is also nearby.
